MagNav.jl¶

MagNav.jl contains a full suite of tools for airborne Magnetic anomaly Navigation (MagNav). The full public API is listed in the API Reference section.

Key functionality of this package is shown on the following pages:

  • Flight Path & INS Data

  • Magnetic Anomaly Maps

  • Aeromagnetic Compensation

  • Navigation Algorithms

There are also multiple example Pluto notebooks available that showcase the various functionalities.

The package is tested with Julia:
